{"word":"αἰσυμνήτης","slug":"αἰσυμνήτης","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>αἰσυμνήτης</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:αἰσυμνάω'><el>αἰσυμνάω</el></a> \n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a regulator</i> of games, <i>a judge</i> or <i>umpire</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>: <i>a president, manager</i>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>an elective prince</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}